PN,43701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FA unique and ancient Cornish moorland
OL,8,Flandscape has become a National Nature
OL,9,FReserve, bringing together more than
OL,10,F1,100 hectares for nature recovery.
OL,12,FThe Mid Cornwall Moors has been
OL,13,Fdeclared the 14th site in the King's
OL,14,FSeries of National Nature Reserves
OL,15,F(NNRs), more than doubling the area of
OL,16,Fland managed for nature in this
OL,17,Fhistoric landscape, with the
OL,18,Fequivalent of 1,500 football pitches
OL,19,Fof moorland.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
