PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FThe declaration aims to improve access
OL,8,Fto nature, create opportunities for
OL,9,Flearning and recreation, and help
OL,10,Fsupport the local economy through
OL,11,Fsustainable farming.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
