PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FThis network includes places that have
OL,8,Fshaped Cornwall's history, spanning
OL,9,Fprehistoric tin streaming, Iron Age
OL,10,Fhillforts and ancient woodland. Iconic
OL,11,Fsites including Helman Tor, the Iron
OL,12,FAge hillfort of Castle an Dinas, and
OL,13,FGoss Moor, known locally as King
OL,14,FArthur's favourite hunting ground, all
OL,15,Fform part of this nationally
OL,16,Fsignificant landscape.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
