PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FThe reserve combines land managed for
OL,8,Fnature and heritage by Natural
OL,9,FEngland, Cornwall Wildlife Trust,
OL,10,FCornwall Heritage Trust, the Gaia
OL,11,FTrust and Imerys. It also includes
OL,12,Fland designated as the Mid Cornwall
OL,13,FMoors Site of Special Scientific
OL,14,FInterest (SSSI), which is land of
OL,15,Fexceptional ecological importance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
