PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FTony Juniper CBE, Chair of Natural
OL,8,FEngland, said: "By bringing these
OL,9,Flandscapes together under one reserve,
OL,10,Fwe are not only helping to restore
OL,11,Fprecious habitats but also creating
OL,12,Fmore opportunities for people to
OL,13,Fconnect with nature, history and the
OL,14,Funique character of this part of
OL,15,FCornwall for generations to come."
OL,17,FNature Minister Mary Creagh said: "The
OL,18,FMid Cornwall Moors is a truly special
OL,19,Flandscape, shaped by thousands of
OL,20,Fyears of history and home to some of
OL,21,FEngland's rarest wildlife.
OL,26,@wD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
