PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,F"Combining this rich patchwork of
OL,8,Fhabitats as a National Nature Reserve
OL,9,Fwill protect this unique place and
OL,10,Fprovide better access to nature for
OL,11,Fthe people who live alongside it and a
OL,12,Fboost to everyone who visits.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
