PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,F`"Reversing the decline in nature and
OL,8,Fmoving toward ecological recovery
OL,9,Frequires bigger, better and more
OL,10,Fjoined up areas for nature to thrive.
OL,11,FWith the support of His Majesty King
OL,12,FCharles III, Natural England is
OL,13,Fleaving a lasting public legacy for
OL,14,Fpeople, science and nature by creating
OL,15,For extending 25 National Nature
OL,16,FReserves by 2028. The Mid Cornwall is
OL,17,Fthe 14th NNR in the Series. Around 1.4
OL,18,Fmillion people live within 5km of a
OL,19,FKing's Series NNR."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
