PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FMatt Walpole, CEO of Cornwall Wildlife
OL,8,FTrust said: "The new Mid Cornwall
OL,9,FMoors National Nature Reserve reflects
OL,10,Fthe importance of long-term
OL,11,Fcollaboration in creating bigger,
OL,12,Fbetter and more connected spaces for
OL,13,Fnature recovery.
OL,15,F"The inclusion of Helman Tor within
OL,16,Fthe National Nature Reserve recognises
OL,17,Fdecades of work to restore habitats
OL,18,Fand support wildlife recovery within
OL,19,Fthis special landscape.
OL,26,@pD@MOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
