PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,F"We are already seeing the benefits of
OL,8,Fworking with natural processes through
OL,9,Fconservation grazing with Longhorn
OL,10,Fcattle and Tamworth pigs, alongside
OL,11,Fpioneering wild beaver
OL,12,Freintroductions. Helping to create
OL,13,Fmore diverse and resilient habitats
OL,14,Ffor wildlife to thrive and for people
OL,15,Fto enjoy."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
