PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1779981070
OL,3,C'A powerful recognition': Ancient
OL,4,Cmoors gain National Nature Reserve
OL,5,Cstatus
OL,7,FCathy Woolcock, CEO of Cornwall
OL,8,FHeritage Trust said: "The Mid Cornwall
OL,9,FMoors National Nature Reserve (NNR)
OL,10,Fbrings together a number of important
OL,11,Fland areas and celebrates both nature
OL,12,Fand the incredible time-depth of human
OL,13,Fhistory, ranging from hunter-gatherers
OL,14,Fin the Mesolithic through to miners
OL,15,Fand farmers in more recent centuries.
OL,17,F"We are pleased that Castle an Dinas
OL,18,Fis to be included within the expanded
OL,19,FNNR, especially given its direct links
OL,20,Fto the Goss Moor and the wider
OL,21,Flandscape in Mid Cornwall.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
